Subject: [PATCH v2 2/2] arm64: dts: ti: k3-am65: Add general purpose timers for am65
Date:   Tue, 30 Aug 2022 10:07:49 +0300
Message-Id: <20220830070750.30640-3-tony@atomide.com>
